  "description": [
    "Page 2 Shake Lewis Works For Hitler Continued From Page il be discontinued until both councils and the Voice of Labor discontinue their attacks against the Inited Mine Workers of America and its officers The District puppets therefore hope to scare the Voice of Labor and the CIO Councils away from the ClOs victory program of all support to President Roosevelt and the nations war effort The Voice of Labor a consistent fighter against fascism at home and abroad ever since its inception live years ago is still committed to the fight against fascism even though John L Lewis is not The CIO Councils are still committed to the fight against fascism even though Lewis is not Lewis Adopts CIO Plan For Joint Committees Lastly the resolution setting off action for Joint Victory production committees at each mine displays the result of rank and file mine workers action for positive winthcwar policies in the United Mine Workers It i worthy to note that the UMWA is far be hind all other TO unions and a great many API unions in the establishment of inductry production plans and the carrying out of the Murray Industry Council Plan introduced more than 1"
